title: Werner to defend top end title
text:
Werner to defend top end title Werner to defend top end title Next Story Prev Story 3 hrs ago Read more: Wimmera Mail-Times 
STATE CHAMP: Emma Werner , is heading back to Darwin to defend her state hammer throw title. Picture: CONTRIBUTED DEFENDING Northern Territory state hammer throw champion Emma Werner will head back to the top end to once again claim the state's top prize.   Wimmera Mail-Times.
